  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the development of algorithms should take into account possible biases and aim to minimize their impact.",
    "Moreover, integrating an understanding of the context into the CMER systems could offer a better interpretation of emotions.",
    "This might involve leveraging auxiliary information or employing more sophisticated models capable of understanding the intricate dynamics of human emotions.",
    "Algorithmic biasAlgorithmic bias [305] poses a significant risk to the integrity of CMER systems.",
    "This bias can stem from either skewed training data or inherent biases in the design of the machine learning algorithms themselves."
  ]
